comments: Mitchell (CLE) brings his off-arm toward Richards (CHA) and marginal contact occurs as Mitchell steps through the double team during the driving shot attempt.
Smith Jr. (CHA) brings his off-arm toward Garland (CLE) and marginal contact occurs as he releases away during the drive.
Okoro (CLE) initiates contact to Hayward's (CHA) front that affects his SQBR during the drive.
Richards (CHA) brings his hands toward Okoro (CLE) and marginal contact occurs as Richards releases away to roll.
Mobley (CLE) legally contests Rozier's (CHA) jump shot attempt.
Rozier (CHA) brings his arm toward Garland's (CLE) path and marginal contact occurs at the start of the drive.
Garland (CLE) brings his off-arm forward and marginal contact occurs with Rozier's (CHA) rested hand during the drive.
Prior to the gather, Smith Jr. (CHA) reaches across and makes contact with Garland's (CLE) hand at the end of his drive.

Replay review of the shooting foul called on Rozier (CHA) pursuant to a coach's challenge was deemed unsuccessful. Rozier (CHA) initiates body contact with Garland (CLE) and affects the follow-through of his driving shot attempt.
Smith Jr. (CHA) inbounds the ball in under 5 seconds.
After the missed shot, the ball deflects off Hayward's (CHA) foot and goes out of bounds.
Smith Jr. (CHA) commits a take foul on Mitchell (CLE).
